This paper deals with the design of mechanisms for finding a committee to optimize the social value in a single-candidate voting system. This involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which are typically studied in the sub-categories of game theory (cs.GT), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
